Date: Wed, 7 May 2025 09:59:19 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 344/376] FROMEXT: LOONGARCH64_NOSIMD: update to 68887137c5

1.Add 2K1000 support
2.Icrease the success rate of download wifi firmware(especially in alpine).

Signed-off-by: maoxiaochuan <maoxiaochuan@loongson.cn>

Link: https://gitee.com/open-loongarch/linux-6.12/commit/043a7bf72c494b9dd3bb00fa483fadf885cea138
Signed-off-by: Mingcong Bai <jeffbai@aosc.io>

Conflict arose because download wifi firmware change was already
 implemented differently upstream.
Resolved by:
- Keeping upstream's version of drivers/net/wireless/realtek/rtl8xxxu/core.c
Link: https://github.com/AOSC-Tracking/linux/commit/0b63d246248f51c211a0626e28f762969343a677
Signed-off-by: Ilikara <3435193369@qq.com>
